{"tid":2106013,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"貿發局宣布因應最新疫情　書展及本月3個活動延期","createTime":"2020-07-13T05:11:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T07:22:22.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"93528770ad765ff9841a6b3a13f26eccf04aa25f","tid":2106013,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T05:11:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537421-20200713.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537421-20200713.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxNVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=c03e7d8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537421-20200713.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=34230893\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537421-20200713.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n貿發局宣布，原定星期三舉行的香港書展和本月三個活動延期舉行。<br />\n<br />\n貿發局表示，過去一個星期新型肺炎確診個案上升，局方曾在過去的周末與特區政府商討，而因應最新疫情發展，政府基於公共健康風險，重新收緊社交距離限制，即使書展已經採取不同的預防措施，亦難以追蹤接觸個案，因此應該避免舉行。<br />\n<br />\n局方表示，市民的健康是首要考慮，因此書展以及另外3個同期舉行的活動，包括香港運動消閒博覽、教育及職業博覽和創業日都會延期。"},{"pid":"9f116e6a5192cb087fc39a58f9762dffcff0a661","tid":2106013,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T05:13:25.000Z","msg":"又縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"908f6bda18613b9951c2c2368bbe8ae8dccc642c","tid":2106013,"uid":15826,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T07:18:43.000Z","msg":"垃圾 等啲書商入哂場開哂檔先講吖笨"},{"pid":"eee7ca21129697567961be67d398c80001f5d537","tid":2106013,"uid":47208,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"908f6bda18613b9951c2c2368bbe8ae8dccc642c","tid":2106013,"uid":15826,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T07:18:43.000Z","msg":"垃圾 等啲書商入哂場開哂檔先講吖笨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T07:22:22.000Z","msg":"我開始覺得功能組別-藝文界果票有望"}]}